-- Merrill says won't sell Bloomberg LP stake
-- 
-- Thu Jan 17, 2008 9:00am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/01/17/us-merrilllynch-bloomberg-idUSWEN344720080117

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Merrill Lynch & Co Inc. on Thursday said it is not interested in selling its 20 percent stake in news and financial data provider Bloomberg LP. 

 Analysts have valued the stake at about $5 billion. There's been speculation Merrill might sell the stake to raise capital. (Reporting by  Tim McLaughlin ; Editing by  Derek Caney )